00:00:17.850 --> 00:00:21.120
discussed in the previous lesson in the form of a flowchart,

00:00:21.120 --> 00:00:24.915
a mindmap, in a list form,

00:00:24.915 --> 00:00:28.575
or in some text editor app like Grammarly.

00:00:28.575 --> 00:00:32.730
Let me give you a very quick overview of these tools.

00:00:32.730 --> 00:00:36.685
The first tool I want to tell you is draw dot io.

00:00:36.685 --> 00:00:40.100
This is used to create flowcharts and I use

00:00:40.100 --> 00:00:43.655
