00:00:43.655 --> 00:00:47.090
It is free to use and it has an offline version as

00:00:47.090 --> 00:00:51.095
well that you can download and install on your computer.

00:00:51.095 --> 00:00:55.789
This is the blank canvas and you can insert shapes.

00:00:55.789 --> 00:01:00.305
Insert text into those shapes by double-clicking at the center,

00:01:00.305 --> 00:01:03.935
arranged them, and make connections.

00:01:03.935 --> 00:01:10.655
Feel free to add as many shapes as you want and arrange the chart in an organized manner.

00:01:10.655 --> 00:01:14.840
You can play with this style and text settings to make it look beautiful.

00:01:14.840 --> 00:01:18.275
And you can also adjust the alignment of the shapes.

00:01:18.275 --> 00:01:23.150
Feel free to explore more shapes and add pages to your document.

00:01:23.150 --> 00:01:26.150
Once you are done, you need not save it

00:01:26.150 --> 00:01:29.930
