00:01:39.365 --> 00:01:44.240
Here you can create mindmaps structures for brainstorming,

00:01:44.240 --> 00:01:46.295
notes, taking, project planning,

00:01:46.295 --> 00:01:48.800
and lots of other creative tasks.

00:01:48.800 --> 00:01:53.960
I use it to create syllabus and curriculum of my courses.

00:01:53.960 --> 00:01:56.810
