00:02:07.730 --> 00:02:11.900
The last tool I want to tell you in this lesson is grammarly.

00:02:11.900 --> 00:02:15.560
It is a writing tool with the Writing Assistant that

00:02:15.560 --> 00:02:19.520
helps you write clear and free from grammatical mistakes.

00:02:19.520 --> 00:02:22.880
I am telling you about gravity because it is the traditional form

00:02:22.880 --> 00:02:26.135
